# Universal Design Rules
- **Typography**: Minimum font size is 18px. Use high-contrast colors (e.g., #000000 on #FFFFFF).
- **Interactions**: All buttons must have a minimum height of 60px for easy tapping.
- **Simplicity**: Avoid complex dropdowns. Prefer vertical lists and large, clear icons with text labels.
- **Language**: Use friendly, simple English. Instead of "Authenticate," use "Sign In."
